body:
### Welcome to SpottyBadRabbit's Blog

For all your trending and cool posts about technology, fashion, music, food and fitness.


### About Me

I am a techno loving food eating fashion fanatic. Who loves to play soccer, snowboard and Brazilian JiuJitsu. Growing up in London, I have a place for grime and EDM but more enthusiastic about "Drill" music and some Bach. Which is a weird mix as they have different textures and rhythm but synonymous seem to go hand in hand.
